	Deprecate Gtk::Main in favor of Gtk::Application.

	* gtk/src/main.[hg|ccg]: Deprecate most of this API.
	* demos/gtk-demo/example_change_display.cc:
	* demos/gtk-demo/main.cc: Use Gtk::Application instead of Gtk::Main.

