	Added class overview documentation for new classes.

	* gdk/src/devicemanager.hg:
	* gdk/src/rgba.hg:
	* gtk/src/buildable.hg:
	* gtk/src/cellarea.hg:
	* gtk/src/cellareabox.hg:
	* gtk/src/cssprovider.hg:
	* gtk/src/numerableicon.hg:
