  CellArea, CellRenderer, Widget: Modify and add some vfuncs.

  * gtk/src/gtk_vfuncs.defs:
  * gtk/src/cellarea.[hg|ccg]:
  * gtk/src/cellrenderer.[hg|ccg]: Add vfuncs get_request_mode,
