	Added methods that use RGBA.

	* gtk/src/colorbutton.[hg|ccg]: Added a constructor taking a Gdk::RGBA, and
	get/set_rgba().
	* gtk/src/cellview.hg: Added set_background_rgba().
	* tools/m4/convert_gdk.m4: Added necessary conversion.

