	* gtk/gtkmm/stock.[h|cc]: Added CAPS_LOCK_WARNING.

	* tools/extra_defs_gen/generate_defs_gtk.cc: Added new interfaces.
	* gtk/src/gtk_signals.defs: Regenerated.

