	* gtk/src/gtk_vfuncs.defs:
	* gtk/src/activatable.[hg|ccg]:
	* gtk/src/orientation.[hg|ccg]: Added the new interfaces, though
	we cannot use them yet without breaking ABI.
	* gtk/src/box.hg:
	* gtk/src/button.hg:
	* gtk/src/buttonbox.hg:
	* gtk/src/menu.hg:
