	GTKMM_API to avoid auto-import errors with gcc on
	mingw32/cygwin. Also inline some TreeViewColumn methods. Bug
	#309030 (Toralf Lund).
	* gtk/src/object.hg: Tag the Object class with GTKMM_API to make
	Visual Studio happy.

